flowchart TD
    Start([horizon logs]) --> GetLines[Get --lines option]
    GetLines --> DetectOS{Detect OS}
    
    DetectOS -->|Linux| Journalctl[journalctl -u orbit-horizon -n lines]
    DetectOS -->|macOS| CheckLogFile{Log file exists?}
    DetectOS -->|Other| UnsupportedMsg[Platform not supported]
    
    CheckLogFile -->|Yes| TailLog[tail -n lines horizon.log]
    CheckLogFile -->|No| NoLogs[No logs found]
    
    Journalctl --> OutputLogs[Output log content]
    TailLog --> OutputLogs
    NoLogs --> OutputLogs
    UnsupportedMsg --> OutputLogs
    
    OutputLogs --> SuccessExit([Success])
